Blogging Website
Project Description
Welcome to the Blogging Website project! This repository showcases a simple yet elegant blogging website, designed and implemented using only HTML and CSS. The website features two main pages: the Home page and the Post page. It also includes icons for popular social media platforms such as Instagram, Twitter, and LinkedIn, enhancing user connectivity and engagement.

Features
Home Page: Serves as the landing page of the blog, displaying a list of recent posts and an introduction section.
Post Page: Dedicated page for individual blog posts, allowing readers to focus on one article at a time.
Social Media Icons: Includes clickable icons for Instagram, Twitter, and LinkedIn, providing easy access to social media profiles.
Responsive Design: Fully responsive layout ensuring optimal viewing experience across a variety of devices and screen sizes.
Technologies Used
HTML: The backbone of the website, structuring the content in a meaningful and accessible way.
CSS: Styles the website, creating an appealing and user-friendly interface.
Screenshots
Home Page
Post Page

Usage
Explore the Home page to see a list of recent blog posts.
Click on any post title to navigate to the Post page and read the full article.
Use the social media icons to visit the corresponding profiles.

